; Enter filtered (disallowed) HOSTNAME patterns in this file
; Wildcard characters (*, ^, ~) are allowed and ! negates the match
; One hostname pattern per line, e.g.: *.some-bad-host.net
; Requires dns_lookup_enabled = yes in botgate_proxy.cfg -- each
; connecting IP is reverse-DNS'd and the resulting hostname (if any)
; is checked against the patterns below. Matches here are logged.
